{"tid":852733,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【曼谷遊客死】逾20人用大口徑手槍槍戰 現場遺AK47子彈","createTime":"2018-10-08T05:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T06:11:54.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"670fce5edea5d6acb89f89f804ea363800b97f5c","tid":852733,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">AK47</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181008/58769468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769468&d=E1%2FwOurwXdkpt3J7pKqlbwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ff748357\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769468&h=1622972f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181008/58769468</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國曼谷水門巿場附近槍戰傷及遊客，造成至少2死5傷，警方初步消息指，爆發槍戰的相信是當地的街頭黨派，多達20名槍手更用上大口徑手槍，包括AK47步槍。<br />\n槍擊案現場位於水門亭閣購物中心（Watergate Pavilion Mall）後附近，警方指，有目擊者見到約20名手持槍械、刀及棍的青年從桌球室衝上街頭槍戰。警方正研究當時他們使用了甚麼槍械，現場初步找到AK47步槍及口徑達9毫米及7.62毫米的彈殼。<br />\n警方指，他們到場時，涉及槍戰的街頭幫派成員已逃走，暫時未知他們的傷亡情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4132ccf38262f0492cced544c4444f649d65cee4","tid":852733,"uid":10890,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老味9mm叫大口徑手槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46615bd22ac74016b6f40b6b34ee387a2d064720","tid":852733,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dis